name: Sky-mobi
overview: Sky Network Technology Co. Ltd was founded in 2005 by a group of young minds filled with enthusiasm and has evolved into the largest company in mobile application software platform in China, which is funded by the legendary US-based Sequoia Capital that also funded companies like Apple, Google, Yahoo! and Cisco. Headquartered in Hangzhou, the company has branches in Beijing, Shanghai and Shenzhen and will set up customer support centers in Indonesia with business operations around the world and customer base extending more than 80 countries and regions. In 2008, the company became one of Top 3 software enterprises in Zhejiang in revenue. With the innovation of China’s “APP Store” concept in 2005, now 4 years have passed, Sky Network has become the most influential enterprise in 3G mobile internet industry with a deep family of products and core technologies that keep ahead both at home and abroad.
